Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.38,0:00:45.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Beats down the sun getting hotter
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:48.87,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Cause these nights won't stay any longer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:50.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I'd rather you near
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:52.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Than far from here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.02,0:00:59.18,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And these streets don't get any longer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.73,0:01:02.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When you're this far from the harbour
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:06.87,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Making it quite hard to sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:09.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And leave my hopes at bay
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:13.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But now I'm gliding through the atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:16.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Bright lights to make it so clear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.96,0:01:20.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I'll travel the stars till I find you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:27.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But these foggy nebulas around me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.49,0:01:30.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Cloud my vision until I can't see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:34.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Still I'll travel alone till' I find home
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:41.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The sunlight it breaks through my cold walls
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.34,0:01:44.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Through open windows, dark frozen halls
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:48.60,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Lighting up the sky, days pass me by~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:54.93,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So I've built a starship in my room
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.20,0:01:58.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To take me to a place I can see you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.69,0:02:02.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Because I cannot cope with my lost hope
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:08.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But now I'm gliding through the atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:12.11,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Bright lights to make it so clear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:16.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I'll travel the stars till I find you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:22.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But these foggy nebulas around me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:26.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Cloud my vision until I can't see
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:30.33,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Still I'll travel alone till I find home~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.13,0:02:50.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,These old nights aren't too nice to~ me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:53.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Left alone oh why can't I see
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:58.14,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Hope that I once had the hope in you~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:04.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But you've opened my eyes to see
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:07.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Stars that glisten all around me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:12.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Hope that I once had has been renewed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:18.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And now I'm gliding through the atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:21.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Bright lights to make it so clear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:25.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I'll travel the stars till I find you~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:32.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Cause I've found by all those around me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:35.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,These future suns are all here to guide me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.05,0:03:39.82,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Through each and every day throw fears away~
